FairSeaBattle 1.0 pre1
----------------------

The FairSeaBattle -- sink the computer's fleet.

    Remember that this versions _is_not_ RELEASE yet.
    It is PRE-RELEASE versions. In an effort to
    provide quality software at release time I will
    PRE-RELEASE one for bug checking. Please submit
    bugs by sending an e-mail to me: a.michurin@gmail.com
    Thanks a lot!

You can get FairSeaBattle here: http://fairseabattle.googlecode.com/

